author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Diamondback Energy Says Produced 102.6 mboe/d oil in Q1
text:
April 10 (Reuters) - Diamondback Energy Inc:
* DIAMONDBACK ENERGY, INC. PROVIDES FIRST QUARTER 2018 PRODUCTION UPDATE
* PRODUCTION FOR Q1 OF 2018 WAS 102.6 MBOE/D (75.6 MBO/D; 74% OIL), AN INCREASE OF OVER 10% FROM Q4 2017 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
